Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都…都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽見了沒
